###################################
# Path shared in host OS
#
# Window Host OS:
# (+) Docker ToolBox:
# Settings of docker-machine VirtualBox Image (default) -> Shared Folders
# -> Add -> Host OS Path -> DockerTLBB -> Auto-mount -> OK
# The env will be:
# SHARED_DIR=/tlgame
#
# Linux Host OS:
# SHARED_DIR=.
#
###################################
